#### 12-level pyramidal deck with different ranks

You can also make an pyramidal deck of 12 levels, where each suit has different ranks. To do it, for every suit pick a different amount of cards: 1, 2, 3, ..., 10, 11, 12. Make sure that the suits that are repeated 12 and 11 times are the 15-ranked suits ({% suit id=0 /%}{% suit id=1 /%}{% suit id=2 /%}{% suit id=3 /%}{% suit id=4 /%}{% suit id=5 /%}{% suit id=6 /%}{% suit id=7 /%}). Each level uses a different suit, and there's no rank indicating how many cards does that level have.

An example game that uses it is [Startups](/games/startups).

